Simple code to search using AngularJs & Sphinx PHP API - SphinxSearch Framework.

Requirements : PHP, Apache, MySQL, SphinxSearch installed and configured on linux.

index.html - Importing angularjs files. Angularjs to look for SearchCtrl as Controller and keywords as input (ng-model) and execute search function on click.

search.js - php file url to send keywords as json and get data to display inside pre.

Search.php - Configuring Sphinx Server credentials like Server IP, Port, Indexes served. Using sphinxapi.php executing query to get results from SphinxServer. Displaying matched ids returned from sphinx daemon.
